-
    Wages chase rent,
  keeping workers in debt.

    Yet rent is zero,
when consumer is owner.

Every worker is a consumer.

So let's gather consumers
  to pay early for products,

 then buy some property
   to escape the usury.

   And trade work early
    for specialization.


